## 2026-04-08 тАФ Session 2

**Tasks completed:** T007, T008, T009 (T009 territory bonuses implemented as part of T007/T008)

**Summary:**
Implemented the full military expansion layer: map grid, fog of war, combat engine, territory bonuses, and military UI panel.

**Files created:**
- `game/src/systems/map.js` тАФ initMap() generates 20├Ч20 tile grid with 5 terrain types; fog-of-war reveal; ~20 enemy settlements seeded; territoryRateBonus() computes per-second rate bonuses from owned terrain
- `game/src/systems/combat.js` тАФ attackTile(x,y) validates adjacency/fog/ownership, sums unit attack with tech multipliers (tactics ├Ч1.25, steel ├Ч1.5, engineering ├Ч1.1), probabilistic outcome (win chance = power/(power+defense)), captures tile + grants loot on win, loses 1 unit on defeat
- `game/src/ui/mapPanel.js` тАФ 480├Ч480 canvas (24px tiles), terrain colour coding, player/enemy tints, fog-of-war blackout, hover highlight on attackable tiles, click-to-attack, live stats bar showing territory/enemy/explored counts
- `game/src/ui/militaryPanel.js` тАФ army summary with total attack power, training queue progress bar, unit training cards (cost/stats/requirements/Train button), building-gate enforcement

**Files modified:**
- `game/src/core/state.js` тАФ added `state.map = null` field; initState() resets it
- `game/src/core/events.js` тАФ added MAP_CHANGED and COMBAT event constants
- `game/src/systems/resources.js` тАФ imported territoryRateBonus(); integrated into recalcRates()
- `game/index.html` тАФ added тЪФя╕П Military and ЁЯЧ║я╕П Map tabs and panels
- `game/src/main.js` тАФ imports initMap, initMilitaryPanel, initMapPanel; calls them in boot(); re-generates map on New Game; saves/loads map in localStorage; save version bumped to 2
- `game/styles/main.css` тАФ full styles for .map-wrap, #map-canvas, .map-legend, .map-stats, .mil-*, .unit-card variants, .log-entry--combat-win/loss

**Architecture decisions:**
- Tile defense scales linearly with distance: `15 + dist * 6` (reachable with 3тАУ5 units at start)
- Combat is probabilistic: `winChance = clamp(0.1, 0.9, power / (power + defense))`
- Territory bonuses are stateless тАФ recalcRates() recomputes from scratch each time; no delta tracking needed
- Map stored in localStorage as part of save state (version 2); backwards compat: if no map in save, initMap() generates fresh one
- Military panel UI fully reactive via existing UNIT_CHANGED / BUILDING_CHANGED events

**Next session should tackle:**
- T011: Tech effects applied more broadly (unit unlock gates, combat tech bonuses visible in UI)
- T013: Random event system (raids, windfalls, droughts)
- T014: Quest/objective system with rewards

