## 2026-04-09 тАФ Session 3

**Tasks completed:** T011

**Summary:**
Completed tech effects system тАФ all research bonuses are now fully wired into gameplay mechanics, UI gates, and display.

**Files modified:**
- `game/src/data/techs.js` тАФ Added 3 new combat techs: `tactics` (+25% attack, requires warcraft), `steel` (+50% attack, requires tactics), `engineering` (+10% attack + Watchtower unlock, requires masonry). Updated `arcane` effectDesc to mention Mage unlock.
- `game/src/data/units.js` тАФ Knight now requires `metalworking` tech; Mage now requires `arcane` tech.
- `game/src/data/buildings.js` тАФ Watchtower now requires `engineering` tech in addition to Wall building.
- `game/src/core/actions.js` тАФ `trainUnit()` applies warcraft -25% speed: `totalTicks = ceil(trainTicks * 0.75)` when warcraft is researched; stores `totalTicks` in queue entry.
- `game/src/ui/buildingPanel.js` тАФ Added `on(Events.TECH_CHANGED, renderBuildingPanel)` so tech-gated buildings unlock immediately on research.
- `game/src/ui/militaryPanel.js` тАФ Imported TECHS; fixed `reqStr` to display tech requirements with icon+name (not raw ID); progress bar uses `current.totalTicks` to handle warcraft speed reduction correctly; army panel now shows tech-multiplied combat power (applying tactics/steel/engineering multipliers).

**Architecture decisions:**
- Combat techs (tactics/steel/engineering) mirror exactly what combat.js already expected тАФ no combat.js changes needed.
