## 2026-04-09 тАФ Session 4

**Tasks completed:** T013, T014

**Summary:**
Implemented the full random event system and quest/objective system, completing Phase 4's two gameplay-enriching features.

**Files created:**
- `game/src/systems/randomEvents.js` тАФ 10 weighted random events (raids/windfalls/disasters), 120тАУ240s interval timer, temporary rate modifier system
- `game/src/systems/quests.js` тАФ 11 milestone quests with check predicates and resource rewards; event-driven completion detection; `setQuestPanelRenderer()` hook avoids circular imports
- `game/src/ui/questPanel.js` тАФ Card grid UI with per-quest completion badge and overall progress bar; wired to QUEST_COMPLETED + relevant events

**Files modified:**
- `game/src/core/state.js` тАФ Added `randomEvents: null` and `quests: null` fields; reset in initState()
- `game/src/core/events.js` тАФ Added `RANDOM_EVENT` and `QUEST_COMPLETED` event constants
- `game/src/systems/resources.js` тАФ `recalcRates()` now applies `state.randomEvents.activeModifiers` rate multipliers (disaster effects); no import needed, reads state directly
- `game/src/main.js` тАФ Imports and wires initRandomEvents/randomEventTick/initQuests/initQuestPanel; registers randomEventTick as 3rd tick system; initRandomEvents() on New Game reset; save version bumped to 4 (adds randomEvents + quests fields)
- `game/index.html` тАФ Added ЁЯПЖ Quests tab button and #panel-quests div
- `game/styles/main.css` тАФ Added styles for .log-entry--raid/windfall/disaster/quest, .quest-header, .quest-list, .quest-card (done/pending variants), .quest-card__* elements, .progress-bar__fill--quest

**Architecture decisions:**
- Disaster modifiers stored in `state.randomEvents.activeModifiers` as `{id, resource, rateMult, expiresAt}` entries; recalcRates() reads them directly тАФ avoids any circular import between randomEvents.js and resources.js
- randomEvents.js imports recalcRates() for immediate effect; recalcRates() reads state.randomEvents without importing the module
- Quest system uses `setQuestPanelRenderer()` callback pattern to let quests.js trigger a UI re-render without importing from questPanel.js
- Quests check on a deferred setTimeout(500ms) after boot so welcome messages appear before any quest rewards that might trigger immediately on load
- Save version 4 is additive; _applySave() uses ?? null defaults so v3 saves load cleanly (just without pre-existing quest/event state)
- Goblin attack has a 40% chance to kill a random unit, making raids have meaningful military consequence; windfalls scale with game tick so late-game rewards stay relevant

